**Bitcoin Money** is a blog relating to various financial aspects of Bitcoin.

The blog's most popular post, [The Rebooting of Money](http://www.bitcoinmoney.com/post/2560941112/rebooting-of-money) is an audio podcast that provides an introduction to Bitcoin.

